name: loading-skin-008-ball-triangle
css: .#= id #-#= loading.id # svg { animation-name: #= id #-#= loading.id #; animation-duration: 2.4s; animation-iteration-count: infinite; animation-timing-function: linear; margin-top: #= loading.itemHeight / -2 #px; position: relative; top: 50%; width: #= loading.itemWidth #px; height: #= loading.itemHeight #px; enable-background:new 35.5 -15.5 38 38; }
@keyframes #= id #-#= loading.id # { from { transform: rotate(0deg); } to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
